3. UNIQUE SELLING PROPOSITION - What makes this DIFFERENT from competitors (be specific)
4. EMOTIONAL TRIGGERS - The emotions that drive purchase decisions for this product
5. SENSORY DESCRIPTION - Specific descriptions of scent, texture, absorption, finish (from real reviews)
6. TARGET AUDIENCE - Who is the ideal customer (age, lifestyle, skin concerns)
